source.name: Maryland Total New Parcels Outside PFA For Residential Development: 2006-2009
source.description:
Maryland Total New Parcels Outside Priority Funding Area (PFA) - New Parcel Development  for Residential Development from 2006 to 2009. 
Priority Funding Areas are existing communities and places where local governments want State investment to support future growth.
